solPicker.filters
Class TMFilter

java.lang.Object
  solPicker.filters.Filter
      solPicker.filters.TMFilter

public class TMFilter
extends Filter

This filter discards oligos whose temperatures are not within a certain range, as specified by the user. The default minimum temperature is 77, and the default maximum is 81. The filter uses an algorithm to calculate the temperature based on the number of G's and C's in each oligo.
